    <author>
      <name>mazenelba</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/779988</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi SAP Community,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;since February 11, 2025, I have been experiencing a &lt;STRONG&gt;403 Forbidden error&lt;/STRONG&gt; when trying to access my &lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Build Apps design-time environment&lt;/STRONG&gt;. The issue also affects my colleague, so it does not seem to be an isolated case.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H4 id="toc-hId-1961023646"&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Error Details:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/H4&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;URL:&lt;/STRONG&gt; &lt;A href="https://a1797de4trial.design-time.us10.apps.build.cloud.sap/builder/projects/?id=us10.a1797de4trial.warehousecontroltower1" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;https://a1797de4trial.design-time.us10.apps.build.cloud.sap/builder/projects/?id=us10.a1797de4trial.warehousecontroltower1&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Error Message:&lt;/STRONG&gt; &lt;EM&gt;"Access to a1797de4trial.design-time.us10.apps.build.cloud.sap was denied. You are not authorized to view this page. HTTP ERROR 403."&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;BTP Subscription:&lt;/STRONG&gt; SAP Build Apps Trial (US10 region)&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Trial Status:&lt;/STRONG&gt; Active&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Browser:&lt;/STRONG&gt; Chrome, Edge (also tested in Incognito mode)&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Tried Solutions:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Checked &lt;STRONG&gt;BTP Cockpit&lt;/STRONG&gt; → &lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Build Apps Subscription is active&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Ensured &lt;STRONG&gt;Role Collections (SAP Build Apps Admin/Developer)&lt;/STRONG&gt; are assigned&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Cleared &lt;STRONG&gt;browser cache &amp;amp; cookies&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Tried with &lt;STRONG&gt;different user accounts&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;This setup has worked fine until last week, and we made no changes to our &lt;STRONG&gt;BTP settings or user roles&lt;/STRONG&gt;.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":pushpin:"&gt;📌&lt;/span&gt; &lt;STRONG&gt;Is this a known issue? Is anyone else experiencing the same problem?&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":pushpin:"&gt;📌&lt;/span&gt; &lt;STRONG&gt;Are there any recent changes to SAP Build Apps that might have caused this?&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Thanks in advance for any help! &lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":smiling_face_with_smiling_eyes:"&gt;😊&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":rocket:"&gt;🚀&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
